    "id": 21,
    "title": "\u269b\ufe0f Post 21: App Router vs Pages Router",
    "text": "\"I deleted my `pages/` directory and it was the best architectural decision I ever made.\"\nWhen building 100+ calculators for calculator-all.com, the legacy Pages router was holding me back. I took the leap to the Next.js App Router, and it completely changed how I think about frontend architecture. \nIf you are still confused about *why* the App Router matters, this carousel is for you.\nSee the App Router speed in action: https://calculator-all.com",
