    "id": 22,
    "title": "\ud83d\udda5\ufe0f Post 22: Server Components vs Client Components",
    "text": "\"React is no longer just a frontend library. It owns the server now.\"\nThe most confusing concept in modern Next.js is the `'use client'` directive. When I built calculator-all.com, I had to decide exactly where the server ended and the browser began.\nUnderstanding React Server Components (RSC) is the key to mastering Next.js. Here is the exact mental model I used to split my logic.\nTest instant Client Components: https://calculator-all.com",
