    "title": "\ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f Post 23: Next.js Image Optimization",
    "text": "\"An unoptimized 2MB PNG will destroy your SEO. Next.js fixes this out of the box.\"\nImages are the #1 reason websites fail Core Web Vitals. But standard `<img>` tags are a thing of the past. \nWhen building calculator-all.com, I refused to let assets slow me down. Using the `next/image` component changed everything. \nHere is how Next.js handles aggressive image optimization automatically.\nExperience perfect loading speeds: https://calculator-all.com",
