  {
    "id": 24,
    "title": "\ud83c\udff7\ufe0f Post 24: SEO with the Metadata API",
    "text": "\"How do you automatically generate perfect SEO for 100 different pages? You let Next.js do it.\"\nTechnical SEO sounds boring until it brings you 10,000 users. \nFor calculator-all.com, I couldn't manually write `<title>` and `<meta>` tags for every single tool. I leveraged the Next.js Metadata API to programmatically dominate search results.\nHere is the blueprint for automating your SEO architecture in Next.js 14+. \nExplore the optimized architecture here: https://calculator-all.com",
