    "id": 26,
    "title": "\ud83d\udcbe Post 26: Demystifying Next.js Caching",
    "text": "\"The most powerful feature in Next.js is also the most misunderstood: Caching.\"\nWhen I launched calculator-all.com, I couldn't understand why my data wasn't updating. I learned the hard way that Next.js aggressively caches everything by default.\nOnce you understand the 4 layers of the Next.js Cache (Request Memoization, Data Cache, Full Route Cache, and Router Cache), you unlock god-tier performance.\nHere is the ultimate cheat sheet to controlling the cache instead of letting it control you. \nExperience aggressive caching speeds: https://calculator-all.com",
